comments: Hachimura (WAS) makes contact to the arm of Harden (HOU) during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Thomas (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Gordon (HOU) and does not deliver contact.
Tucker (HOU) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Thomas (WAS) and does not affect his SQBR.
Gordon (HOU) and Bryant (WAS) engage and disengage during the rebound.
Bryant (WAS) jumps vertically and maintains a legal vertical position as he contests Harden's (HOU) shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, it is determined that the ball was not in the cylinder during the Westbrook (HOU) tip-in and the basket counts.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Thomas (WAS) is the last player to make contact with the ball prior to the ball going out of bounds.
Gordon (HOU) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Beal (WAS) and does not deliver contact.
Harden (HOU) makes marginal contact with Bertans (WAS) during his drive but does not dislodge him from his legal guarding position.
Bryant (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Gordon (HOU) and does not deliver contact.
Tucker (HOU) makes contact to the arm of Beal (WAS) during his shooting motion that affects his play at the basket.
Gordon (HOU) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Bonga (WAS) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Bertans (WAS) makes marginal body contact with Harden (HOU) during his shooting motion that does not affect his play at the basket.
Bryant (WAS) makes contact to the body of Westbrook (HOU) after the release that affects his play at the basket.
Gordon (HOU) maintains a legal guarding position as he defends Beal (WAS) and does not affect his SQBR.
Thomas (WAS) commits a take foul on Tucker (HOU).

Replay review of the foul called on Tucker (HOU) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  Tucker (HOU) does not maintain a legal guarding position and makes contact to Beal's (WAS) arm, which affects his upward shooting motion.
Bonga (WAS) makes contact to the body of Harden (HOU) during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Harden (HOU) makes incidental contact with Hachimura (WAS) after he loses possession of the ball.
